org.apache.spark.streaming

Class TestOutputStreamWithPartitions<T>

  • Object
      • org.apache.spark.streaming.TestOutputStreamWithPartitions<T>

  • public class TestOutputStreamWithPartitions<T>
extends
    This is a output stream just for the testsuites. All the output is collected into a ArrayBuffer. This buffer is wiped clean on being restored from checkpoint.

    The buffer contains a sequence of RDD's, each containing a sequence of partitions, each containing a sequence of items.
